<p source="SHANGBO.ZHAOWANGHUISHI 4.17.1 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 4: 50"><pb xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.1">昭王為室於死湑之淲</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.2">室既成,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.3">將落之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.4">王戒邦大夫以飲酒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.5">既,行(=將)落之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.6">王入將落,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.7">有一君子喪服蹣廷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-1a.8">將跖閨</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHAOWANGHUISHI 4.17.2 (STRIPS 1-2) JI XUSHENG 4: 50"><pb xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.1">侍(雉?)人止之曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.2">君王始入室,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.3">君之服不可以進</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.4">不止曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.5">小人之告窆將斷於今日</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.6">爾必止小人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-2a.7">小人將肇寇</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHAOWANGHUISHI 4.17.3 (STRIPS 2-4) JI XUSHENG 4: 50"><pb xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.1">侍(雉?)人不敢止.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.2">至閨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.3">卜令尹陳省為視日,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.4">告:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.5">僕之毋辱君王,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.6">不幸僕之父之骨在於此室之階下</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.7">僕將斂亡老</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.8">[...] 以僕之不得併僕之父母之骨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-3a.9">私自敷.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHAOWANGHUISHI 4.17.4 (STRIPS 4-5) JI XUSHENG 4: 50"><pb xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.1">卜令尹不為之告.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.2">“君不為僕告,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.3">僕將肇寇.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.4">卜令尹為之告.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.5">[王]曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.6">“吾不知其爾墓,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.7">爾姑須.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.8">既落焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0046_tls_001-4a.9">從事.”</seg></p>

